org.dblp.mmdb

Interface RecordDbLocalInterface

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    RecordDbInterface
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RecordDb

    public interface RecordDbLocalInterface
    The local query interface for accessing dblp records from a dblp record DB structure.

      • getCoauthorCommunity

        java.util.Collection<Person> getCoauthorCommunity(Person person,
                                                  int index)
                                           throws java.lang.NullPointerException,
                                                  java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException
        Retrieve a specific coauthor community of a given person. Disambiguation profiles are considered to be valid coauthor nodes that link the network.
        Parameters:
        person - The person.
        index - The community index.
        Returns:
        The coauthors of this community.
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if the specified person is null.
        java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException - if the index is out of range (index < 0 || index >= getNumberOfCommunities())

      • getCoauthorCommunityIndex

        int getCoauthorCommunityIndex(Person person,
                              Person coauthor)
                       throws java.lang.NullPointerException
        Retrieve the community index of a coauthor of a given person. Disambiguation profiles are considered to be valid coauthor nodes that link the network.
        Parameters:
        person - The central person.
        coauthor - The coauthor to look up in the coauthor communities of person.
        Returns:
        The community index between 0 and getNumberOfCommunities()), or -1 if no such coauthor exists.
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if one of the specified persons is null.
